name: NWProtocolWebSocket.CloseCode
desc: Types of codes used upon closing a WebSocket connection.

items.name: init(rawValue: UInt16)
items.desc: Initializes a close code with a raw value.

items.name: case protocolCode(NWProtocolWebSocket.CloseCode.Defined)
items.desc: A well-known close code reserved by the protocol (values 1000-2999).

items.name: case applicationCode(UInt16)
items.desc: A close code in the range reserved for applications and frameworks (3000-3999).

items.name: case privateCode(UInt16)
items.desc: A close code in the private-use range (4000-4999).
